      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/AgamaH/AryaH/hinduism/sAmya-vaiShamye/tattvam/sangrahaH/laxmIpura-shrInivAsa-mAna-meya-rahasya-shloka-vArttikam/07_sambandhaH/053_sambandhavAdaH/383_vAchyavAchakabhAvaH/</guid>
      <description>&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;मूलम्&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;वाच्यवाचकसंबन्धनिषेधे लोकबाधनम् । विरोधश्च स्ववाक्येषु किं कथं प्रतिपाद्यते ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;मूलम्&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;औत्पत्तिकस्सामयिक इति वादोऽत्र भिद्यते ।प्रथमो वैदिकः पक्षः द्वितीयो यौक्तिको मतः ॥&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
